00:27:22.050 --> 00:27:24.500
And it can last
more than one year.

00:27:24.500 --> 00:27:26.280
It can be two or
three years in a row.

00:27:26.280 --> 00:27:31.630
So that's-- I think it takes
a lot of conviction that

00:27:31.630 --> 00:27:34.150
you're on the right path, and
you're doing what you think is

00:27:34.150 --> 00:27:36.140
best for, you know,
your partners.

00:27:36.140 --> 00:27:42.210
And I think, if the
principles are sound,

00:27:42.210 --> 00:27:45.220
eventually they will work out.

00:27:45.220 --> 00:27:48.340
So again, the
importance of patience--

00:27:48.340 --> 00:27:51.260
I think that's probably the most
important quality you need when

00:27:51.260 --> 00:27:53.190
you invest in the stock market.

00:27:53.190 --> 00:27:55.980
SPEAKER 1: So to people who
